
---

# ✅ CLEAN .gitignore

Replace ENTIRE `.gitignore` with this:

```gitignore
# Python
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Node
node_modules/

# Environment files
.env
.env.*

# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Build folders
build/
dist/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# OS files
.DS_Store